street-tax-arrival = [color=#f5b942]SCANNER:[/color] A small booster crew is moving through the market lanes with the confidence of people collecting protection money.
street-tax-shakedown = [color=#f5b942]SCANNER:[/color] Raised voices and forced smiles detected. Someone is being reminded who owns this block tonight.
street-tax-compliance = [color=#f5b942]SCANNER:[/color] The locals fold. Credit chits change hands and the pressure starts to bleed off.
street-tax-violence = [color=#ff4444]ALERT:[/color] The shakedown broke bad. Weapons are out and the block just turned hot.
street-tax-retreat = [color=#f5b942]SCANNER:[/color] The collectors are peeling away from the scene before heavier response arrives.
